com.github.nwillc.ksvg.elements

Enum SVG.RenderMode

  • Enclosing class:
    SVG

    public static enum SVG.RenderMode

    The mode to employ when rendering. Some Elements must render differently when used inline in HTML5 or in a standalone SVG file.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      FILE
      Render as an SVG .svg file format.
      INLINE
      Render as inline SVG designed to appear inline in HTML5.
